OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy day with outbreaks of
OL,6,Frain, this turning heavy at times. A
OL,7,Ffew limited brighter intervals in
OL,8,FMoray, where it could be quite warm.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FA mainly cloudy evening and
OL,11,Fnight with showery outbreaks of rain,
OL,12,Fthese occasionally on the heavy side.
OL,13,FBecoming rather murky with risk of
OL,14,Fmist and fog patches developing.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FVariable cloud with afternoon
OL,17,Fshowers developing, some heavy and
OL,18,Fmerging into longer spells of rain,
OL,19,Fwith a risk of thunder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
